CLIENT SETUP
1. Open sns-stripe/package.json
2. Change REACT_APP_API_URL to the address of the server
3. Change REACT_APP_STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY to your Stripe public key
4. Run 'npm run start' from sns-stripe/

SERVER SETUP
1. Open backend/.env
2. Change STRIPE_PUBLISH_KEY to your Stripe public key
3. Change STRIPE_SECRET_KEY to your Stripe secret key
4. Change OUTPUT_FILE to where you want to keep the registry of payments
5. Run 'npm run start' from backend/

STRIPE SETUP
1. Go to your Stripe dashboard -> Developer view -> Webhooks view
2. Add a webhook endpoint: '<server address>'/webhook 
    (e.g., http://localhost/webhook)
3. Have it listen to at least 'payment_intent.succeeded'
